div.pre:
SELECT
U.COUNTRY,
COUNT(*) AS TOTAL_EVENTS,
COUNT(CASE WHEN E.EVENT_TYPE
= 'page_view' THEN 1 END)
AS PAGEVIEW_COUNT,
COUNT(CASE WHEN E.EVENT_TYPE
= 'purchase' THEN 1 END)
AS PURCHASE_COUNT
FROM RAW_EVENTS E
INNER JOIN USERS U
ON E.USER_ID = U.USER_ID
GROUP BY U.COUNTRY
ORDER BY TOTAL_EVENTS DESC;
